---
import { experience, highlights, skills } from '../../data/site'
---
<section id="about" class="relative px-6 py-24 md:px-12 md:py-32 lg:px-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16">

      {/* LEFT: narrative */}
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-ink mt-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
          A quiet executor
          <br />
          <span class="serif-italic text-spotlight-soft">who likes the boring wins.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col text-ink-muted mt-8 gap-5 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I have spent the past five years helping teams turn search from a
            guessing game into a&nbsp;
            <span class="serif-italic text-ink">reliable channel</span>
            . That has meant late nights in log files, painstaking redirect maps,
            and a lot of rewriting product copy that nobody else wanted to touch.
          </p>
          <p>
            The work I am proud of does not look exciting on a slide. It looks like
            a clean indexation chart, a steadily climbing keyword cohort, and revenue
            you can trace back to a specific cluster of pages we shipped six months ago.
          </p>
          <p>
            I work with one or two clients at a time so the people paying me actually
            get me, not an account manager. If we work together you will have my
            number, my Slack, and my honest opinion when something is a bad idea.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Highlight stats: hairline rail, not chips. */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-t border-line mt-12 gap-y-8 gap-x-10 pt-10 sm:grid-cols-4">
          {highlights.map((h) => (
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
              <span class="num-display text-ink text-3xl md:text-4xl">{h.value}</span>
              <span class="font-mono uppercase text-ink-muted text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.18em]">{h.label}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* RIGHT: experience timeline + skills */}
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:col-span-5">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Where I've been</span>
          <ol class="flex flex-col mt-6">
            {experience.map((item, idx) => {
              const borderCls = idx === experience.length - 1 ? 'border-b' : '';
              return (
                <li class={`group relative flex items-baseline justify-between border-t border-line transition-colors duration-300 gap-4 py-5 hover:bg-surface-raised/40 ${borderCls}`}>
                  <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                    <span class="font-serif text-ink text-xl tracking-[-0.01em]">{item.role}</span>
                    <span class="text-ink-muted text-sm">{item.company}</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-mono uppercase text-ink-muted shrink-0 text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.22em]">{item.period}</span>
                </li>
              );
            })}
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">The toolbox</span>
          <ul class="flex flex-wrap mt-6 gap-x-2 gap-y-2">
            {skills.map((skill) => (
              <li class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-line font-mono text-ink-muted transition-colors duration-300 bg-surface-raised/40 px-3 py-1 text-[0.7rem] hover:text-ink hover:border-ink/30 hover:bg-surface-raised">
                {skill}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
